{"name":"Ambient Power","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-blue.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 3 Arcane Advance</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>Arcane 8</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>You gain a +3 bonus to your Arcane rolls to cast every spell beyond the first one on your turn.</p>","xpCost":550,"hpBonus":1,"fpBonus":4},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iHtNj6ddSOhgavRy"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768054308472,"modifiedTime":1774471826157,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"6azRl2d49YTzDxX7"}
{"name":"Arcane Wellspring","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-explosion.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 4 Arcane Advance</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:&nbsp;</strong>Arcane 10,&nbsp;<em>Ambient Power</em></p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>The focus cost of every spell you cast on your turn beyond the first one is reduced by one-quarter of the total. This effect applies after any other modifications to the focus cost.</p>","xpCost":750,"hpBonus":2,"fpBonus":5},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.0I599oIxuPl0qGn3"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768054204590,"modifiedTime":1774471860683,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Z0kqIdxJqxBiKdo8"}
{"name":"Mana Flow","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-teal.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 5 Arcane Advance</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Arcane 12, <em>Ambient Power</em></p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>The AP cost of every spell you cast on your turn beyond the first one is reduced by 1, to a minimum of 1.</p>","xpCost":1100,"hpBonus":3,"fpBonus":8},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.0RAHULVa0aAx5cwO"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767962414627,"modifiedTime":1774471872342,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"b2DYajXjb7LO2vfp"}
{"name":"Spell Memory I","type":"advance","img":"icons/tools/scribal/ink-quill-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uHLLY2mwwXAMMg4v"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-fee9acb5-7fff-b9e5-5174-f0783b63ae22\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Tier 1 Arcane Advance</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Prerequisites:&nbsp;</strong>None<br><strong>Effect: </strong>You gain the ability to cast Rank 1 spells. You can prepare up to one Rank 1 spell each time you memorize spells for the day. You may take this advance multiple times, adding a new Rank 1 slot each time.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br><br></p>","xpCost":150,"hpBonus":0,"fpBonus":2},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472206551,"modifiedTime":1774472206551,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"cNwtRWL04E3oEdRV"}
{"name":"Spell Memory II","type":"advance","img":"icons/tools/scribal/ink-quill-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.A3HkAWIqViAVoxKJ"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-fee9acb5-7fff-b9e5-5174-f0783b63ae22\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Tier 2 Arcane Advance</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Prerequisites:&nbsp;</strong>Spell Memory I<br><strong>Effect: </strong>You gain the ability to cast Rank 2 spells. You gain a Rank 2 spell slot, with which can prepare one Rank 2 or lower spell each time you memorize spells for the day. You may take this advance multiple times, adding a new Rank 2 slot each time.</p>","xpCost":250,"hpBonus":0,"fpBonus":2},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472208011,"modifiedTime":1774472208011,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"hR8BV3qGeTOcjdBj"}
